        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/c/d07c76/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2023-04-01T13:47:50.422Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Amazing about the Aligote.<br>\nDavid is such a nice and good guy.  Also he\u2019s a confident and super competent wine maker.  Got to spend some time speaking with him recently at the NYC La Paulee verticals.  We hadn\u2019t seen each other in years and amazingly he immediately recognized me/remembered my name.</p>",
